message.entry: Invalid string input. Type help primpoly for more information on usage.
Invalid string input for polynomial display option.\nChoose ''nodisplay'' to turn off polynomial form of display.
M must be a real positive scalar greater than 0 and lesser than or equal to 16.
Third parameter must be the string ''nodisplay'' to turn off the display the polynomials naturally
Weight L must be a real positive scalar.
No primitive polynomial satisfies the given constraints.
